 Men\">The Lusty Men</a></i> (1952)</li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/wiki/Johnny_Guitar\" title=\"Johnny Guitar\">Johnny Guitar</a></i> (1954)</li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/wiki/Run_for_Cover_(film)\" title=\"Run for Cover (film)\">Run for Cover</a></i> (1955)</li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/wiki/Rebel_Without_a_Cause\" title=\"Rebel Without a Cause\">Rebel Without a Cause</a></i> (1955)</li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/wiki/Hot_Blood\" title=\"Hot Blood\">Hot Blood</a></i> (1956)</li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/wiki/Bigger_Than_Life\" title=\"Bigger Than Life\">Bigger Than Life</a></i> (1956)</li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/wiki/The_True_Story_of_Jesse_James\" title=\"The True Story of Jesse James\">The True Story of Jesse James</a></i> (1957)</li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/wiki/Bitter_Victory\" title=\"Bitter Victory\">Bitter Victory</a></i> (1957)</li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/wiki/Wind_Across_the_Everglades\" title=\"Wind Across the Everglades\">Wind Across the Everglades</a></i> (1958)</li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/wiki/Party_Girl_(1958_film)\" title=\"Party Girl (1958 film)\">Party Girl</a></i> (1958)</li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/wiki/The_Savage_Innocents\" title=\"The Savage Innocents\">The Savage Innocents</a></i> (1960)</li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/wiki/King_of_Kings_(1961_film)\" title=\"King of Kings (1961 film)\">King of Kings</a></i> (1961)</li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/wiki/55_Days_at_Peking\" title=\"55 Days at Peking\">55 Days at Peking</a></i> (1963)</li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/wiki/We_Can%27t_Go_Home_Again\" title=\"We Can&#39;t Go Home Again\">We Can't Go Home Again</a></i> (1976)</li>\n<li><i><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Lightning Over Water</a></i> (1980)</li></ul>\n</div></td></tr></tbody></table></div>\n<div role=\"navigation\" class=\"navbox\" aria-labelledby=\"Wim_Wenders\" style=\"padding:3px\"><table class=\"nowraplinks collapsible autocollapse navbox-inner\" style=\"border-spacing:0;background:transparent;color:inherit\"><tbody><tr><th scope=\"col\" class=\"navbox-title\" colspan=\"2\"><div class=\"plainlinks hlist nav